// caseworker_permit  (kind: permit  ·  validation: FAIL_ON_ANY_FINDINGS)
// A benefits caseworker may use the governed tools. Deny-by-default is automatic at the
// AgentCore Policy engine; this is the only broad grant. The principal is authorized by the
// Cognito group claim surfaced as a tag — no group, no access.
permit(principal, action, resource is AgentCore::Gateway)
when {
  principal.hasTag("cognito:groups") &&
  principal.getTag("cognito:groups") like "*benefits_caseworker*"
};
